OOC: No, well, yes, sort of, He, Denzabar, shares his spark with a council 
member, or elder, ( Forgive me, I forget their names) And can freely enter the 
matrix to help heal or find sparks. The fact he sharesa a spark is known, but 
the exact reason isn't known yet, also right now his memory is sort of 
rebooting, so, random images may pop up as well.

BIC: "Calm down? How?" Denzabar said, still lifeless but voice. He stopped 
talking for a few...."Ok, This is a Predacon program, how do I know 
that...Embrace the program, don't delete it."

--part1_79.1b49ea0b.2cc65973_boundary
